. Vi m\u00e5 ogs\u00e5 \u00e5 bli flinkere til \u00e5 jobbe med alternativer til sykmelding, som \u00f8kt tilrettelegging p\u00e5 arbeidsplass, sier J\u00f8rgensen.", "Les ogs\u00e5: Uf\u00f8repensjonist anmeldt for svindel av 1,3 mill."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "pluss"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "c68b47c86cf5d2e2ff38cccf6052517a762b926a92132b44546082b48b1b7b33"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2015-08-27T20:43:24.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Leger m\u00e5 t\u00e5le \u00e5 bli sett mer i kortene, s\u00e6rlig n\u00e5r de sykmelder folk over lengre tid, sl\u00e5r Nav fast."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/pluss/article11474976.ece/1mbmgv/ALTERNATES/w980-default/NAV1.jpg"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/32d064bdd74085ab729a42f9e629ea3b01b94e97.jpg?596a8908"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["Nav vil overpr\u00f8ve legens sykmelding oftere -adressa.no", "Pr\u00f8veprosjekt i Hedmark", "Underviste studenter", "NTNU + Nav"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "32d064bdd74085ab729a42f9e629ea3b01b94e97"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["Nav", "NTNU", "St. Olavs Hospital"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "Nav,NTNU,St. Olavs Hospital"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": "pluss"}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": ["careers", "education"]}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["overpr\u00f8ve legens sykmelding", "sykmelding", "lege", "overpr\u00f8ve legens", "legens sykmelding oftere"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["nav", "sverige og nederland", "adresseavisen", "u. h\u00e5pet", "nederland og sverige"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": ["hedmark", "s\u00f8r-tr\u00f8ndelag", "sverige", "norge"]}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": ["karen walseth hara", "hanne kristine j\u00f8rg